Even though I was reeled in by the cute characters and the futuristic hi jinks, part of my mind was fixated on how the world turned to refuse and how everybody got so lazy and fat. 

The viewer focussed on the negative points. The waste on the planet and the fat people are negative points. The viewer focussed on the negative aspects despite good character creation and futuristic elements within the plot.

